OL,3,CMan killed in Spanish wildfire as
OL,4,Cscorching weather grips Europe
OL,6,FThe Spanish capital and parts of
OL,7,FFrance and Turkey are battling
OL,8,Fdangerous conditions and fires, as ITV
OL,9,FNews' Lora Jones reports.
OL,11,FAt least one person has been killed in
OL,12,FSpain as wildfires continue to burn
OL,13,Facross Europe.
OL,15,FAuthorities confirmed the death as a
OL,16,Fwildfire swept through more than 2000
OL,17,Facres of land just outside of Madrid.
OL,19,F12 fire engines and three helicopters
OL,20,Fwere at the scene,
