OL,3,CMan killed in Spanish wildfire as
OL,4,Cscorching weather grips Europe
OL,6,FFirefighters have worked to tackle the
OL,7,Fblaze and have begun letting residents
OL,8,Freturn to their homes.
OL,10,FElsewhere, temperatures are expected
OL,11,Fto climb to 44 degrees Celsius in some
OL,12,Fparts of Spain as emergency services
OL,13,Fcontinue to battle wildfires in
OL,14,Fseveral Spanish regions.
OL,16,FSeveral fires have forced thousands of
OL,17,Fpeople to evacuate, including
OL,18,Fholidaymakers in Cadiz on Monday.
