OL,3,CMan killed in Spanish wildfire as
OL,4,Cscorching weather grips Europe
OL,6,FIn Portugal, more than 700
OL,7,Ffirefighters worked to control a fire
OL,8,Fin Trancoso, around 200 miles
OL,9,Fnortheast of Lisbon.
OL,11,FOn Monday, fires in the suburbs of
OL,12,FMontenegro's capital, Podgorica,
OL,13,Fspread overnight, forcing authorities
OL,14,Fto call for international help.
OL,16,FNumerous buildings were evacuated as
OL,17,Fseveral homes burned.
OL,19,FThere were also major fires in coastal
OL,20,Ftowns, but no casualties were reported.
