OL,6,FFires spread through the suburbs of
OL,7,FMontenegro's capital on Monday as the
OL,8,Fcountry's authorities called for
OL,9,Finternational help.
OL,11,FScientists have warned that climate
OL,12,Fchange is exacerbating the frequency
OL,13,Fand intensity of heat and dryness
OL,14,Facross the South of Europe.
OL,16,FIt's making the area more vulnerable
OL,17,Fto extreme heat and wildfires.
OL,19,FThe continent is warming up faster
OL,20,Fthan any other in the world.
